Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.91,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121413,124916}Metropolitan Entertainment approached Maya,\Nwho has just entered high school…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.79,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:124916,127794}…about an audition for "The Miracle Worker".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:13.46,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:127794,133467}Maya declines out of fear\Nof losing to her rival, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:20.22,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:133467,140223}Miss Tsukikage threatens to expel Maya\Nunless she gets the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:27.23,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141224,147230}{\an5\pos(766,680)\fscy95\blur1\fad(0,0)}—Episode 18—\NThe Challenge of Helen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149733,155447}Metropolitan Entertainment has chosen you five\Nas the candidates for the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157199,159910}Shiratori Reina,\Nfrom Kaze Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160410,162913}Hayakawa Akiko,\Nfrom Tenma Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163330,167584}We recognize both of your\Nachievements on TV series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167584,170003}Kanaya Emi, who is a member of the\Nacting group of Hitotsubashi High School…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170003,174091}…and whose talent is\Nhighly recognized by the critics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174341,178970}Next, we do not need an introduction\Nfor Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183850,187729}Last, but not least, Kitajima Maya\Nfrom Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190982,193317}The audition is set for August 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198824,202202}Ayumi, is it true that you moved\Nout of your mother's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202202,204329}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204329,208500}Why? You can get advice from\Nyour mother, should you live with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208500,211795}That's right. And you can practice\Nfor "The Miracle Worker" together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214297,217342}That's the reason\NI moved out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217342,220679}I don't need my mother's\Nreputation to get this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220679,223098}I will win this role solely with my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224099,226643}Ayumi,\Nwhat a strict person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.69,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:230230,234693}"The Miracle Worker" is an inspiring\Nand touching drama about a girl Helen Keller…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.44,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:234693,237446}…who can't hear, see, nor speak…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:05.78,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:237446,245787}…but comes to understand words through\NMs. Sullivan's passionate and persistent education.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:16.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:249875,256423}When school got out for summer break, Maya\Nstarted practicing everyday at the church with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256590,259050}Sit still and eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259050,261845}Fold the napkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261845,263346}Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263346,264931}Wait, Helen!\NHelen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266725,271480}Don't run away from me.\NYou are not done eating yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271480,273940}Helen, come back—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277152,278736}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278736,281156}Why did you look at me, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281948,284701}Helen can not hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288038,290707}Here, Maya, become Helen now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293043,293627}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294586,297214}Walk as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297214,299591}Get mad as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299591,301176}Eat as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301176,304095}Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304596,308433}Now, Maya, play as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308433,310060}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310060,312479}Now, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313939,315649}Play as Helen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:20.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315649,320946}Play as Helen, who is blind, deaf,\Nand not able to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320946,326117}If you can't do that, you will never\Nknow the real Helen. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326117,329996}Teacher, that's enough.\NI can practice with her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332624,335460}Yeah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335460,337462}What?\NYou're tearing the church down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337462,340382}Yeah, haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340382,343218}A mansion is going to be built here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343218,348223}No way.\NThis is our practice hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352143,354020}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357274,360610}What a patient she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360610,365740}If she continues like this,\Nshe'll never get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:09.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365740,369828}Teacher is ill,\Nand the practice hall is gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369828,372247}What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390181,393894}I have a report about the five\Ncandidates for Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393894,394895}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396563,401359}Shiratori Reina is getting\Nstrict training at her theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405238,410952}Hayakawa Akiko is actually playing\NHelen Keller with her acting group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412495,417208}Kanaya Emi is in libraries\Ndoing research about Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417208,423965}And Himekawa Ayumi is volunteering at\Nan agency for disabled children like Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425091,426927}As for Kitajima Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429179,434851}…the church she was practicing at was demolished\Nand now she doesn't have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451659,453495}Maya, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453495,454704}Look, it's Mr. Purple Rose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454704,456247}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:43.88,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:458875,463880}{\fad(0,1500)}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462921,465173}"I believe it's hot in Tōkyō now."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465173,469260}"If it's not too much, I would like to invite you\Nto my summer house in Nagano."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469260,470303}Summer house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472806,475767}Wow, there's a train ticket, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478311,480730}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480730,481815}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483316,486528}I'll go and practice\NHelen's role there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:13.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487821,493909}"I will not be able to be there,\Nbut my friends will look after you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496746,500875}Mr. Purple Rose always helps\Nme out whenever I'm in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500875,503378}He's like my guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.72,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:512220,516725}{\fad(1500,0)}Bidoro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513096,516975}Hey, Sakurakōji.\NYou should have came a day earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516975,517851}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517851,521688}You know, Mr. Purple Rose.\NShe got an invitation from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529988,534074}Maya, I can't do anything\Nfor you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545086,546129}How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548715,550759}Hi there, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550759,554012}I'm Yamashita, the house sitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554012,557432}I'm Kitajima Maya.\NIt's very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557432,559851}Here, come on in.\NWe've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564439,565982}Wow, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565982,568860}It's bright and has\Na beautiful view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568860,570695}Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570695,575992}We live right down the street, so please\Ndon't hesitate to come to us if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575992,579621}Of course, we'll come by to clean\Nand prepare meals, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579621,582165}Oh, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582165,583958}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583958,587087}What is the owner of this house like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589130,593093}Oh, by the way, he told us\Nto give you the flowers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:01.60,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:597680,601601}Ms. Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602268,605271}"I hope you will have\Na wonderful time."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605271,610318}"I do have one wish:\Nplease don't ask around about me."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612278,613655}"—Mr. Purple Rose".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623248,626960}I understand.\NI won't ask about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626960,630588}I will win Helen's role here.
Comment: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:45.72,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:645728,645728}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:49.52,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:649524,649524}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:52.48,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:652485,652485}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656656,659784}Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659784,661161}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661161,663246}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663246,667333}It's a nice day today.\NYou should go outside and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667333,668168}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668168,671754}A young girl should not stay home all day. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671754,672922}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684809,688396}A yacht and a sailboat,\Nhorse back riding and cycling…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688396,690732}I'm sure Helen\Ndidn't play this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693359,698364}Teacher, I suggest we take turns\Ngetting off work to go see Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698364,702285}I'm sure it's hard\Nto practice without a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702285,706247}No, being Helen\Ndoesn't require a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706247,708917}She's better off by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708917,710627}By herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713713,717300}Yes.\NAll by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:03.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719636,723598}Helen… I still don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:06.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723598,726017}What was your everyday life like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726017,728353}How did you spend a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731814,732857}Helen…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734400,736736}Helen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740281,742867}I got it.\NI'll live as Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746704,747914}Some cotton…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751459,754002}…and some dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754002,755546}Helen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:41.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756881,761469}I'll live as Helen,\Nin the darkness and silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777443,780530}Maya, Maya.\NMaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780530,784450}It's strange, dear.\NAll the windows are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784450,785785}Here, let me have the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785785,786869}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790665,792667}It's dark in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792667,794752}Maya, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797463,800717}Oh!\NWhat the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806014,806806}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806806,807932}Upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825950,827994}Ma-Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830913,832040}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:58.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833207,838296}Who?\NA touch, but whose hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842842,845136}Oh, the caretakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845845,847513}What's wrong, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847513,850600}What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854520,862653}Do · not · wo·rry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862653,869118}This · is · prac·tice · for · my · act·ing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876209,880963}Say, dear, she says not to worry,\Nbut do you think she's really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880963,882423}Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:47.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883466,887303}They came,\Nthat means morning is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888304,890264}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937603,939397}Here it is!\NThe fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969093,971012}I wonder what time it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971012,973890}Night, or day?\NOr morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976309,979562}Many thoughts come\Nto me as I sit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981314,984567}Sakurakōji.\NHow is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984567,986611}Teacher and Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:29.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986611,989030}It feels so long\Nsince I last saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994160,995661}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995661,998623}You have been missing,\Nbut where are you, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998623,1000708}I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025399,1028694}Business is well this summer,\Nhuh, Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028694,1030238}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030238,1034784}This party of yours, with many celebrities\Nfrom Metropolitan Entertainment…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034784,1037537}…has become a popular tradition in Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039830,1041832}It's good advertisement for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041832,1044585}Many big names from the economic\Nand political worlds are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044585,1048881}So, as artists, your reputation shall surely flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051467,1056722}You make anyone\Na tool of your business, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056722,1059725}Do you have anyone without business ties?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060059,1062603}Him?\NOf course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063854,1069151}You'll choose a woman with the most advantages\Nfor your business for your future wife, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069151,1070611}What, are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070611,1072071}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072071,1076325}I will be very careful in choosing,\Neven using a computer if I have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076325,1078578}…for a person who is suitable\Nfor Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078578,1079620}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080454,1081831}Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081831,1082790}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082790,1086586}The house sitter of your summer house\Nwants to see you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091340,1093968}I've never seen him lose his cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:36.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113613,1116824}I knew to be careful\Nwhen coming down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120161,1122288}Ouch!\NI can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122288,1123789}I must have sprained my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124832,1127668}I wonder how long\NI've been doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127668,1129420}Yet I still can't learn her ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:52.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129420,1132214}Helen's life, Helen's play…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133049,1134716}I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134716,1137970}I want to take the earplugs\Nand blindfold off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137970,1141098}I want to hear, see and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141098,1142558}I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:06.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144393,1146228}I'm taking this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151359,1153819}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153819,1157281}I will never understand\Nhow Helen feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:23.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159116,1163329}Whatever happens, I will stay\Nlike this until I learn her ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176716,1178969}Who?\NWhose hand is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178969,1181347}Not the caretaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183349,1184308}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192149,1193943}Oh, a rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:02.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198823,1202326}It's a rose.\NMr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:15.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204245,1215923}Are · you · Mr. · Pur·ple · Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:34.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230438,1234150}Finally!\NI finally get to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:41.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234150,1241282}The person who has been encouraging me\Never since my first stage appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241282,1244618}The person who is always on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244618,1247788}Thank you.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247788,1249081}Little girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:07.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264054,1267641}What was that?\NHe just held me and…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281489,1285201}W-Wait!\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285201,1287703}Please tell me, just your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287703,1290915}I appreciate you with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290915,1294502}Every time I'm about to give up,\NI always think about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294502,1297880}Please, please tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303010,1315022}I · am · look·ing · for·ward\Nto · see·ing · your · Hel·en.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317817,1319151}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328077,1329537}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332121,1334416}Something's wrong with you,\NHayami Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:17.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334416,1337211}She's a girl more than ten years\Nyounger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:20.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337211,1340506}Being the person that I am,\Nbeing the person that I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341549,1344510}"I am looking forward\Nto seeing your Helen."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:26.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1344510,1346971}"I am looking forward\Nto seeing your Helen"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:30.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348180,1350975}I'll do it.\NI won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:33.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350975,1353269}I'll become Helen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:38.56,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1355479,1358566}Maya has finally met\NMr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:43.98,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1358566,1363988}It was a mysterious meeting,\Nbut it became an inspiration for Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:46.28,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1363988,1366282}…who struggles to understand Helen.
Comment: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:50.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370452,1370452}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:03.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377669,1383799}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:09.88,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383799,1389889}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:21.89,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389889,1401899}{\blur3}Something calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:34.03,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401899,1414039}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.91,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1414039,1419919}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:46.04,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419919,1426049}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:52.13,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426049,1432139}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:58.22,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432139,1438229}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:04.23,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438229,1444239}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:10.19,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1444239,1450199}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
